            <title>[SOLR-2945] Solr war maven artifact is not signed by &apos;ant sign-artifacts&apos;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2945</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Because &lt;tt&gt;*.war&lt;/tt&gt; is not included in the set of patterns of artifacts to be signed in &lt;tt&gt;sign-artifacts-macro&lt;/tt&gt; in &lt;tt&gt;lucene/common-build.xml&lt;/tt&gt;, the &lt;tt&gt;solr-X.Y.Z.war&lt;/tt&gt; maven artifact isn&apos;t being signed by &lt;tt&gt;ant sign-artifacts&lt;/tt&gt; when run under &lt;tt&gt;solr/&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
